<statement>
<p>Which of the following is largest amount (rather than largest percent)? </p>
<p><ol style="list-style-type:upper-alpha"><li>3<percent/> of 2622</li> 
<li>84<percent/> of 80</li> 
<li>28<percent/> of 243</li> 
</ol></p>


</statement>
<solution>
<p><ul><li>A: 3<percent/> of 2622</li></ul></p><p>We must first calculate (or at least approximate) each value.</p>
<p>
  <m>\displaystyle{84}\%\cdot{80}={67.2}</m></p>
<p>
  <m>\displaystyle{28}\%\cdot{243}={68.04}</m></p>
<p>
  <m>\displaystyle{3}\%\cdot{2622}={78.66}</m></p>
<p>From these calculations we see that 3<percent/> of 2622 is the largest.</p>

</solution>
